		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=247125"><span id=Scholar>Jiggidyjay of the Seven Seas</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br /><img alt="Avatar" height="50" width="50" src="/uf/Jiggidyjay/Flippie_20_Spammer.gif"><br /><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*"/><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />1669 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [3.52]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Jiggidyjay&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p><a href="HTTP://www.magecompendium.com/" target="akztarg">The Mage's Compendium</a> is the place you want to go.<br /><br />1. The delay does not matter. The damage of the weapon must be more then double the damage of what the pet would do barehanded for it to use the weapons damage. So, if you pet does 10 damage barehanded, the weapon needs to do 21 (good luck on that one) for the pet to use the weapons damage. The big hoohah about pet toys is mostly for the stats (like HP and haste) and for big weapon procs (pets proc like crazy).<br /><br />2. They have all of the armor and weapon slots. I'm not sure about range and charm slots, but I wouldn't think so. You can have a higher level mage (or yourself!) summon phantom armor and other stat increasing gear to give your pets and others pets.<br /><br />3. Answered at the top.</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006062&resize=true" target="akztarg">Jiggidyjay</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Ranger</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1003866&resize=true" target="akztarg">Zingin Ansinging</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Bard of <a href="HTTP://firestormers.com/viewnews.php" target="akztarg">The Firestormers</a></span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006061&resize=true" target="akztarg">Zolotaya</a> - <span class="sm">Ms Necro</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1189723" target="akztarg">Zeibis</a> - <span class="sm">Monk</span></td></td></tr><